58 /* This module was send to me my Pat Richards <patr@x509.com> who
59 * wrote it. It is under my Copyright with his permission. */
60
61#include <openssl/x509.h>
62#include <openssl/asn1t.h>
63
64
65ASN1_SEQUENCE(NETSCAPE_SPKAC) = {
66 ASN1_SIMPLE(NETSCAPE_SPKAC, pubkey, X509_PUBKEY),
67 ASN1_SIMPLE(NETSCAPE_SPKAC, challenge, ASN1_IA5STRING)
68} ASN1_SEQUENCE_END(NETSCAPE_SPKAC)
69
70IMPLEMENT_ASN1_FUNCTIONS(NETSCAPE_SPKAC)
71
72ASN1_SEQUENCE(NETSCAPE_SPKI) = {
73 ASN1_SIMPLE(NETSCAPE_SPKI, spkac, NETSCAPE_SPKAC),
74 ASN1_SIMPLE(NETSCAPE_SPKI, sig_algor, X509_ALGOR),
75 ASN1_SIMPLE(NETSCAPE_SPKI, signature, ASN1_BIT_STRING)
76} ASN1_SEQUENCE_END(NETSCAPE_SPKI)
77
78IMPLEMENT_ASN1_FUNCTIONS(NETSCAPE_SPKI)
